The number is larger than the maximum allowed.\nThe answer to the quiz is incorrect.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nThe e-mail address entered is invalid.\nThe URL is invalid.\nThe telephone number is invalid.', 'contato-pt', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-form-1', '', '', '2019-04-01 09:51:47', '2019-04-01 12:51:47', '', 0, 'http://avaliacao.test/?post_type=wpcf7_contact_form&#038;p=7', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
